      "review_summary": "The PR adds `channels[\"*\"].ackReaction` validation, runtime fallback, selected scanner exclusions, and focused tests for wildcard channel config.\n\nPR surface: Source +46, Tests +184. Total +230 across 11 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-level: current main and `v2026.6.9` reject `channels[\"*\"]` during validation and do not read it in `resolveAckReaction()`. I did not run a live gateway in this read-only review.",
